{\fs24\cf1\b SNESAmp v3.1\par}
{Super NES® APU emulator plug-in for Winamp\par}}
{\par
SNESAmp is a plug-in for Winamp that emulates the audio processing unit (APU) of the Super Nintendo
 Entertainment System®.  Its purpose is to allow you to play music from video games.\par\par
SNESAmp can play both SPC's (APU dumps from emulators) and ZST's (ZSNES save states).  SPC files can
 also be contained in RAR files with an .RSN extension.\par\par
You can learn more about how to use SNESAmp by clicking on the Contents button above.\par\par

